<item>
            <title>[LOG4J2-2925] FAQ has broken link formatting for SLF4J link</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-2925</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://logging.apache.org/log4j/2.x/faq.html#gc-free-slf4j&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://logging.apache.org/log4j/2.x/faq.html#gc-free-slf4j&lt;/a&gt; has broken link formatting for the link to SLF4J&apos;s &lt;tt&gt;LocationAwareLogger&lt;/tt&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;org.slf4j.spi.LocationAwareLogger::log&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;#log(org.slf4j.Marker, java.lang.String, int, java.lang.String, java.lang.Object(&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.slf4j.org/api/org/slf4j/spi/LocationAwareLogger.html[&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://www.slf4j.org/api/org/slf4j/spi/LocationAwareLogger.html[&lt;/a&gt;], java.lang.Throwable)) method is &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;...&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Interestingly GitHub renders the link &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/logging-log4j2/blob/master/src/site/asciidoc/faq.adoc#is-log4j-2-still-garbage-free-when-i-use-the-slf4j-api&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;without issues&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And additionally the URL is incorrect, it should be (i.e. without spaces / &lt;tt&gt;%20&lt;/tt&gt; between the method parameters):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
http:&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//www.slf4j.org/api/org/slf4j/spi/LocationAwareLogger.html#log(org.slf4j.Marker,java.lang.&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;,java.lang.&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;,java.lang.&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Object&lt;/span&gt;%5B%5D,java.lang.Throwable)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
